All Classes and Interfaces

Class
Description
AbstractGenericSvc<P,Q>
Implementation of AbstractSvc for generic messages.
AbstractSvc<P,Q>
Abstract implementation of Service.
AuthenticationSvc
Extends AbstractSvc to provide a concrete implementation of the WS defined to authenticate:
"https://cfdidescargamasivasolicitud.clouda.sat.gob.mx/Autenticacion/Autenticacion.svc"
Authorization
Authorization contains the token provided from SAT to access massive download web services.
Batch
Batch downloads all available digital certificates (CFDIs) from the BatchSolicitudes it receives through a map; and saves the download status of each solicitude in a file that can be uploaded later and continue each download process where it left off.
Batch.DownloadHandler
Implementation of DownloadListener that uses a specified BatchWriter to write all download events that are notified to it.
BatchException
Base class for Batch process exceptions, which is usually an Exception wrapper.
BatchFactory
BatchFactory provides a Builder to create a Batch instance with download requests along with a file; which you can use with this factory's BatchFactory.load(java.io.File) method to load a Batch instance in the state it concluded last time executed.
BatchReader
BatchReader provides methods to parse BatchRequests and EventResponses contained in Nodes of a SOAPMessage generated and saved to a file by a BatchWriter.
BatchReader.DisposedResponse
Extends DescargaResponse to be able to be created with a disposed state.
BatchReader.RequestsIterator
This class implements a BatchRequest iterator, parsing requests from a specified Node iterator.
BatchRequest
BatchRequest is used to identify and locate a specific request and its data, within a Batch that holds several requests.
BatchSolicitude
BatchSolicitude extends DefaultSolicitude to implement a Solicitude that can be downloaded; has an additional identifier, and adds new public methods that update this solicitude with responses received from the web service.
BatchWriter
BatchWriter formats a file with a SOAPMessage containing the requests included in a Batch object, and adds the responses received from the web service to the message that is then updated in this writer's assigned file.
CertUtils
Helper methods for loading certificates and private keys from files.
Client
Client is an implementation of DMTClient that calls DMTService in order to consume the massive cfdi download service.
Credentials
Credentials contains the methods needed in order to sign SOAP requests for the massive cfdi download service, for a singular contributor.
CredentialsProxy
Abstract implementation of Credentials.
CredentialsStore
A storage for Credentials.
DefaultMessageFactory
Default implementation of SvcMessageFactory to provide methods needed to build and sign messages.
DefaultSolicitude
DownloadRequest (Solicitude) implementation.
DefaultSolicitude.EmptyRegistry
Utility class that provides a concrete implementation of MutableRegistry representing an empty download registry.
DefaultSolicitude.MutableRegistry
MutableRegistry extends interface DownloadRegistry adding a method that allows changing the download state of a package identifier.
DefaultSolicitude.VerifiedRegistry
Concrete implementation of MutableRegistry that represents a download registry that can be updated.
Delay
Values for the state of the Delay.
DescargaResponse
Represents a response of SAT's massive download web service, when requesting the download of a particular package
DescargaSvc
Extends AbstractGenericSvc to provide a concrete implementation of the WS defined for downloading specific packages:
"https://cfdidescargamasiva.clouda.sat.gob.mx/DescargaMasivaService.svc"
DMTClient
DMTClient contains methods needed for a contributor to download cfdis, and store them, at particular stages of the download process.
DMTService
DMTService includes the methods that consume the SAT's cfdis massive download web service.
DownloadContext
Methods that class DownloadState requires to make requests to SAT and process the responses received.
DownloadEvent
Represents and event generated after receiving a response from the web service.
DownloadEvent.Result
Result values of a download event from the WS
DownloadEventException
RuntimeException that denotes an error produced during a download event.
DownloadListener
Defines an object which listens for DownloadEvents.
DownloadRegistry
DownloadRegistry contains methods to view the download statuses of the package identifiers to be downloaded to complete the download request.
DownloadRegistryImpl
Implementation of DownloadRegistry.
DownloadRepository
Repository that stores downloaded packages
DownloadService
Default implementation of DMTService to consume the WS.
DownloadState
Abstract class representing the state of a download request solicitude.
DownloadState.Accepted
Concrete implementation of DownloadState that represents the accepted state of a download request.
DownloadState.Delayed
Implementation that overrides DownloadState.Accepted to represent the delayed state, which is when the verify request service has been called and the web service has responded that the verification is not yet ready.
DownloadState.New
Concrete implementation of DownloadState that represents the initial state of a request that has not been sent to the service.
DownloadState.Verified
Concrete implementation of DownloadState that represents the verified state of a download request.
EventResponse
EventResponse is a web service response derived from a download event with additional properties that facilitate its manual serialization.
LocalRepository
Download repository implementation that saves downloads in a specified directory.
OasisSecurity
Utility methods for signing envelopes according to the security requested by the WS of CFDI downloads.
PackageIds
This class containing the names or ids of the packages to be downloaded from SAT.
Query
Defines methods needed to create a request to the massive download web service.
QueryMap
Query mplementation that uses a QueryMap.Builder class to create SAT query requests.
QueryMap.Builder
Provides methods for building Queries.
RealCredentials
This class is an implementation of Credentials that uses a private key in order to implement the sign method.
RepositoryException
Base class for Repository related exceptions Note: this is a RuntimeException
SatResponse
Abstract base for responses received from the SAT web service.
Service<P,Q>
Interface that defines the method and parameters needed to implement a service that consumes a massive download SAT web service.
SOAPUtils
Helper class that provides simple methods for parsing SOAPMessages; converting messages to String or from String; and saving or reading them from file.
SolicitaResponse
SolicitaResponse is SAT's response from a download request to the massive download web service when requesting a download for the first time of a particular query.
SolicitaSvc
Extends AbstractGenericSvc to provide a concrete implementation of the WS defined for requesting downloads:
"https://cfdidescargamasivasolicitud.clouda.sat.gob.mx/SolicitaDescargaService.svc"
Solicitude
Represents a download request to the massive download web service, with its status and information that is collected as the steps are invoked to download the digital certificates.
SolicitudeData
Contains the information collected from a request at different stages.
SolicitudeData.Delayed
Contains the information collected from a Solicitude whose request has not yet been verified.
SolicitudeData.Verified
Contains the information collected from a Solicitude whose request has been verified.
StateValue
Values of a Solicitude state.
SvcMessageFactory
Defines methods needed to build and sign messages.
SvcParseException
Exception representing a problem or error while parsing a soap message.
SvcSignatureException
Exception indicating problems or failures while signing a SOAP request.
SvcSignatureFactory
Provides digital signature related methods needed for the WS this package was made for.
VerificaResponse
VerificaResponse is SAT's response from a "verify download request" made to the massive download web service when requesting a verification for a particular request mapped by a requestId or (IdSolicitud) provided in a download request of a particular query.
VerificaResponse.Builder
Utility class to facilitate creation of VerificaResponse instances.
VerificaSvc
Extends AbstractGenericSvc to provide a concrete implementation of the WS defined for verifying download requests:
"https://cfdidescargamasivasolicitud.clouda.sat.gob.mx/VerificaSolicitudDescargaService.svc"
